---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read Shelby Web Company's Privacy Policy for how we collect, use, and protect information for website visitors and clients."
>
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 px-4" data-animate>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-brand-glow text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-sky/80 text-lg mb-2">Effective Date: July 3, 2026</p>
      <p class="text-brand-sky/70 leading-relaxed">
        Shelby Web Company respects your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what choices you have.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-10 text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed">
      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We may collect the following categories of information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Contact details you submit, such as name, email, phone number, company name, and project details.</li>
          <li>Business information related to your services, goals, and marketing needs.</li>
          <li>Usage and technical data, such as IP address, browser type, device details, pages viewed, and referring pages.</li>
          <li>Communications you send us through forms, email, chat, or phone.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Respond to inquiries and provide requested services.</li>
          <li>Prepare proposals, onboard clients, and manage projects.</li>
          <li>Improve website performance, usability, and security.</li>
          <li>Send service-related updates and relevant marketing communications.</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations and enforce agreements.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">3. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to analyze traffic, remember preferences, and improve user experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Trusted service providers supporting web hosting, analytics, communication, invoicing, or project delivery.</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law or to protect rights and safety.</li>
          <li>A successor entity in connection with a merger, acquisition, or business transfer.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">5. Data Retention and Security</h2>
        <p>
          We retain information only as long as needed for legitimate business purposes or legal requirements. We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards to protect your data, but no method of transmission or storage is completely secure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">6. Your Choices</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">You may request to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Access, update, or correct your information.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information, subject to legal and operational requirements.</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing emails by using the unsubscribe link or contacting us directly.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our site may include links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-dark/60 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact Shelby Web Company at
          <a href="mailto:dx1creations25@gmail.com" class="text-brand-cyan hover:text-brand-glow transition-colors">dx1creations25@gmail.com</a>
          or
          <a href="tel:+17044738188" class="text-brand-cyan hover:text-brand-glow transition-colors">(704) 473-8188</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
